3"},{"v":"Stage 3"},{"v":"Stage 1"},{"v":"On the Hill: Teach position words and simple sentences, e.g., \u0022The cow is on the hill.\u0022\n\u2022 Head, Shoulders, Knees and Toes: Teach body parts, e.g., \u0022This is my nose.\u0022 | \u0022These are my arms.\u0022\n\u2022 Colors: Teach color vocabulary and preferences, e.g., \u0022What color do you like?\u0022 - \u0022I like red.\u0022\n\u2022 Teddy Bear (Feelings): Teach emotions and the difference between he and she, e.g., \u0022He is sad.\u0022 / \u0022She is happy.\u0022\n\u2022 Teddy Bear Song: Teach action phrases, e.g., \u0022Turn around,\u0022 \u0022Touch the ground,\u0022 etc.\n\u2022 Ice Cream: Teach likes and doesn\u0027t like, e.g.,\n\u0022My mommy doesn\u0027t like ice cream.\u0022 / \u0022I like ice cream.\u0022  \n\u2022 What do you see?: make a sentence with \u0022I see\u2026\u0022"},null,null,null,null,null,null,{"v":"Ok"},{"v":"Date(2026,5,4,19,16,0)","f":"04/06/2026 19:16:00"},{"v":"Ok"},null,{"v":"Pass"},{"v":"NGUYỄN VÕ HIẾU ĐẠT - 0908178722"},{"v":"Date(2026,2,14,8,26,16)","f":"14/03/2026 08:26:16"},{"v":"VIBHA THAKUR - 0898225427"},{"v":"Date(2026,5,4,19,16,8)","f":"04/06/2026 19:16:08"},{"v":"Date(2026,4,12,15,37,0)","f":"12/05/2026 15:37:00"},{"v":"2026"},{"v":"06"},{"v":"Week 23 (01/06 - 07/06)"},null,null,{"v":"Mr. Đạt- New (14/03/26-08:26)\nMr. Đạt- Change (03/06/26-16:19)\nMs. Vibha- Completed (04/06/26-19:16)"}]},{"c":[{"v":"HDK2TTEDOA|9AE2B514"},null,{"v":"HDK2TTEDOA"},{"v":"HD | I. Kid 2 (Fox) - TTE (Cucumber) Ms. Đoan"},{"v":"1. Registered"},{"v":"Hưng Định (HD)"},{"v":"TRẦN KHÁNH ĐOAN - 0901652907"},{"v":"Ms. PHAN PHÚC KHƯƠNG (02052020) , Ms. THÁI NGỌC HÀ ANH (25102020) , Mr. TRẦN NGUYỄN ANH KHÔI (28092020) , Ms. NGUYỄN KHÁNH NGÂN (06122019) , Ms. NGUYỄN MINH ANH (18102020) , Mr. MAI QUÂN KIỆT (02012021)"},null,{"v":"Thu"},{"v":"Date(2026,5,11)","f":"11/06/2026"},{"v":"Thu - 11/06/2026 | 17:45 - 19:15"},{"v":"Date(1899,11,30,17,45,0)","f":"17:45:00"},{"v":"Date(1899,11,30,19,15,0)"